Crowdsourcing is a great way to provide datasets for machine learning projects.

We ask our users to provide specific types of data that will meet the need of our customers.

So you don’t have to worry about finding or creating that dataset.

Focus on your models only. Leave the rest to us.

We know that the internet does not always provide you the perfect datasets.

Especially if your challenge is to gather specific data,

it is harder to find anything that will satisfy your requirements.

Our users are eager to help you solve this problem.

Our users are aware that they help us solve a great problem by taking the data set out of the equation.

What is even greater is it is also a source of income for users.

Unlike common belief, we think AI will create new employment types, e.g., data supervision and actuation.
